description: There is NO WRESLTING in this update. This is a behinds the scenes glimps of how we book and train our girls. Sometimes a booking goes smoothly without any hiccups and sometimes Murphy's Law kicks and and it seems like nothing can go right. See how we fill in cancellations and train our girls who have never wrestled before. This is completely PG, no nudity, no wrestling. It tells the story of how we do things. A bonus for the Ultimate Fan
title: Behind the Scenes: Booking Ultimate Surrender: The making of a match: NO WRESTLING
